This project is for simulating dice rolls in 8th edition of Warhammer
40,000. The goal of this is to have a way to do statistical analysis
of units to determine how effective/viable they are. As a Necron player,
expect to features helping analyze Necron units (e.g. tesla rules) before
others. 

The directory structure is:

README
LICENSE
src/
	wh40kutils	# the main module for the backbone of rolling
	test		# directories for tests as needed
	sample		# Misc code making use of this module.